<section class="ww-section" id="about">
  <div class="ww-container ww-grid12">
    <div class="ww-eyebrow-row" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
      <span class="ww-eyebrow"><span class="ww-idx">01</span> &nbsp; About</span>
      <span class="ww-bar"></span>
      <span class="ww-eyebrow">Who is doing this, and why.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="ww-about__lede">
      <p>
        Zak Winnick builds charging infrastructure for a living, owns the EVs
        he reviews, and is learning to fly. The channel is what happens when
        one person has too many opinions and too many cameras.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most charging YouTubers test plugs. I test the parking lot, the lighting,
        the sign placement, the canopy, the bid documents, the host's attitude.
        The plug is the easy part.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most ownership content is a manufacturer review wearing a casual jacket.
        I've been in EVs since 2014, across three vehicles and most of the major
        networks. I'll tell you what a decade of charging stops actually feels like.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="ww-about__sidebar">
      <dl>
        <div>
          <dt>Day Job</dt>
          <dd>Founder and CEO, <em>Rangeway Energy</em></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Community</dt>
          <dd>
            Community Director, <a href="https://bayarearivianclub.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bay Area Rivian Club</a>
            <br />
            Executive Director - <a href="https://norcalevs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NorCal EVs</a>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Podcast</dt>
          <dd>Host - <a href="#podcast">Wyld Wramblings</a></dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt>Lives in</dt>
          <dd>Napa, CA</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </aside>

    <div class="ww-about__portrait">
      <img
        src="/images/zak-portrait.jpg"
        alt="Zak Winnick at Vasquez Rocks, R1T behind"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        width="1600"
        height="1200"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
